Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libcurl4 (>= 7.68), libssl3 | libssl1.1, libsqlite3-0 (>= 3.31)
Maintainer: OpenClaw Project <openclaw@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw
Description: OpenClaw AI Assistant â€” native Linux implementation
 OpenClaw is a personal AI assistant with CLI, gateway daemon,
 and kernel module for Linux. It provides:
  - CLI binary for direct AI API interaction with streaming
  - Gateway daemon with epoll-based HTTP server
  - WebSocket support for real-time chat
  - Kernel module for /dev/oclaw IPC and netfilter hooks
  - OpenAI-compatible API endpoint
  - SQLite session storage
  - systemd integration with watchdog support
